{"tid":222381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藏獒vs比特犬，邊隻贏","createTime":"2017-04-29T13:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T14:31:08.000Z","uid":107983,"like":165,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"223ae864d1688e2845524653288188f3d1ec3c6b","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"藏獒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">藏獒性格兇猛，野性尚存，因此出現多起藏獒傷人甚至死亡的事件，又有一獒抵三狼的美譽。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkXWnwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkXWnwH.jpg&h=4eba1f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4786pi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4786pi5.jpg&h=8490badb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比特犬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">比特犬性情兇猛，對陌生人有敵意，對飼主忠誠。比特犬㹴屬於「格鬥狗隻」，打鬥時睾丸激素分泌速度較其他犬種快，高濃度的睾丸激素使它不怕疼痛，因而可以持久戰鬥</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82p687q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82p687q.jpg&h=1f0f484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JBg87R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JBg87R.jpg&h=7ed95834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62Xu4SH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62Xu4SH.jpg&h=0432b754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c5e26f9f1ed12afd6739dcc4c079eb864be0a33","tid":222381,"uid":46845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"狗王之戰"},{"pid":"00fde3a79cc54aed2938fdd0c94bf007294e9b18","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ＝比特犬<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＝藏獒"},{"pid":"b9884d14f1a3ae6c6dea312d5905f0d18f53bbdf","tid":222381,"uid":61832