g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無未必 係比特必定贏 比特除左肌肉 好撚大力之外 打交上黎完全係喪 完全唔理自己會唔會死  <br />\n睇過段片比特咬實左隻狗 啲人點打點踢都唔鬆嘴 胡椒噴霧同電擊棒都無用<br />\n 好撚恐怖 係可以狂電9佢都唔理唔放口"},{"pid":"46a4178e6d2251b1d3a5c5659e23c3e4688cd9a5","tid":222381,"uid":24074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>額外資訊<br />\n藏獒咬合力:84.5802公斤<br />\n比特犬咬合力:86.43252公斤</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"71c42bc2cd6d49c5f537f2cfc30ee78df4dcc81d","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>額外資訊<br />\n藏獒咬合力:84.5802公斤<br />\n比特犬咬合力:86.43252公斤</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n已經唔誇，洛威拿　咬合力134.263341633公斤，家犬中最高"},{"pid":"6895f3e0812c2697ab05f247446d09b2f59db929","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比特贏撚硬<br />\n爆晒肌肉<br />\n係戰爭機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又未必，藏獒大隻個比特犬好多，體格上已經有差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無未必 係比特必定贏 比特除左肌肉 好撚大力之外 打交上黎完全係喪 完全唔理自己會唔會死  <br />\n睇過段片比特咬實左隻狗 啲人點打點踢都唔鬆嘴 胡椒噴霧同電擊棒都無用<br />\n 好撚恐怖 係可以狂電9佢都唔理唔放口</blockquote><br />\n但係唔好忘記藏獒體型上有壓制，大家咬合力又差唔多，如果比特犬比隻藏獒壓低左再咬住條頸理得佢抗擊打勁唔勁，咪又係要死"},{"pid":"da480d424331b48dca3a3b58da1dd068830449af","tid":222381,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔識野<br />\n<br />\n想問下瑞典獵鹿犬點?<br />\n識人係瑞典養左隻純種既<br />\nWiki話佢以前用黎捕熊,鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c77676f641a77ec1f1659c65217cdc1243af9c","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識野<br />\n<br />\n想問下瑞典獵鹿犬點?<br />\n識人係瑞典養左隻純種既<br />\nWiki話佢以前用黎捕熊,鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實際體形、咬合力唔清楚嘅時候好難用以前用嚟捕熊呢件事做對比，而且又有可能係十幾隻一齊圍上去先係捕熊，不過就咁睇用一拳嚟做比喻瑞典獵鹿犬會係Ｂ級實力，藏獒同比特犬個啲會係Ｓ級實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbc967013ffc6105a56e15bade51aa36cc0a292","tid":222381,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T20:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔識野<br />\n<br />\n想問下瑞典獵鹿犬點?<br />\n識人係瑞典養左隻純種既<br />\nWiki話佢以前用黎捕熊,鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實際體形、咬合力唔清楚嘅時候好難用以前用嚟捕熊呢件事做對比，而且又有可能係十幾隻一齊圍上去先係捕熊，不過就咁睇用一拳嚟做比喻瑞典獵鹿犬會係Ｂ級實力，藏獒同比特犬個啲會係Ｓ級實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b18084f2d4827a6f2b8cd3deeab37525ae298a","tid":222381,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"結論：藏獒必勝，我大天朝神犬萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c069a0551fec3451b7d9dfe0659344a4d3c4005e","tid":222381,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比特贏撚硬<br />\n爆晒肌肉<br />\n係戰爭機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又未必，藏獒大隻個比特犬好多，體格上已經有差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"